<div><head>《陸氏異林》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.2">鍾繇嘗數月不朝會，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.3">意性異常。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.4">或問其故，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.5">云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.6">「常有好婦來，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.7">美麗非凡。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.8">問者曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.9">「必是鬼物，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.10">可殺之。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.11">婦人後往，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.12">不即前，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.13">止戶外。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.14">繇問何以。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.15">曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.16">「公有相殺意。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.17">繇曰，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.18">「無此。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.19">乃勤勤呼之；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.20">乃入。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.21">繇意恨恨，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.22">有不忍之心，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.23">然猶斫之傷髀。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.24">婦人即出，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.25">以新綿拭血，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.26">竟路。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.27">明日，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.28">使人尋跡之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.29">至一大冢，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.30">木中有好婦人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.31">形體如生人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.32">著白練衫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.33">丹繡兩當，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.34">傷左髀，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.35">以兩當中綿拭血。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.36">叔父清河太守說如此。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.37">《魏志‧鐘繇傳》注、《御覽》八百十九又八百八十七。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.38">裴氏松之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1502_CHANT_001-1a.39">「清河陸雲也。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
